<p class="pCodeShiftBottom"></p>
<a name="wp3744354"> </a><p class="pBody" >
Ensures that <code class="cCodeBody">addr</code> does not underflow (i.e., change from a value of 3 at the rising edge of <code class="cCodeBody">clk</code> to a value of 7 or a value less than 3 at the next rising edge of <code class="cCodeBody">clk</code>).  </p>    <div align="left"><img src="images/ovl_checkers52.gif" height="83" width="448" border="0" vspace="0" hspace="100" />  </div>	
